{"tid":118251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"李斯特城上年拎冠軍 其他隊真係要檢討下","createTime":"2017-02-13T00:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T17:28:58.000Z","uid":27485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"491b8677c3ba0f1cbe6207015b84232a3ad0b21c","tid":118251,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"上年半季之後其實李斯特城已經下滑左<br />\n場場都係一球上落<br />\n但熱次 同 死阿狗都唔爭氣<br />\n講實力上年熱次其實仲勁<br />\n係衰唔穩定 輸完比車仔 仲比紐卡素炒<br />\n阿狗仲衰 西布朗個堆都贏唔到<br />\n上年咁都贏唔到 黎緊幾年都好難贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92486caaae5eef5c976e5d7646c045b5d6968de","tid":118251,"uid":57049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"成季淨係輸過俾利物浦同阿仙奴算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今季對中堅退化得咁快都要長前出現係場上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d5313b4a012f71c92ffff68b9b1fb76a3d3aed","tid":118251,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"係度賴上年靠黑哨先拎英超 有好多強隊都攻唔入又守唔住 關人黑哨咩事"},{"pid":"5dbd45d6a4af1e7a662ed25855a78d1917b243f6","tid":118251,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:04:29.000Z","msg":"Kante"},{"pid":"d3c8cbcd4cecf10f517719fc192fed316e5e14df","tid":118251,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"今年冇食藥"},{"pid":"403b096c84769eec7b1216ef5784aed498ddf70d","tid":118251,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd055354d319c72e422a6e275080115f3c9f6f91","tid":118251,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"我廠舊年都雙殺隊垃圾啦"},{"pid":"1f312e4d76c1ce222902be1e693f1bc3c54d8246","tid":118251,"uid":61279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-